<emphasis bold="true" box="[163,340,3085,3119]" pageId="17" pageNumber="614">Distribution.</emphasis>
Aberdare Range and Mt Kenya, C Kenya.
</paragraph>
</caption>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="17" pageNumber="614" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="17.[2057,2652,293,721]" pageId="17" pageNumber="614">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[2060,2340,293,327]" pageId="17" pageNumber="614">Descriptive notes.</emphasis>
Head-body 108-139 mm, tail 42-88 mm, ear 16-3-20-5 mm, hindfoot 19-23-2 mm; weight 34-70 g.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="17" pageNumber="614" type="biology_ecology">
