<subSubSection pageId="17" pageNumber="614" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="17.[1446,2653,741,917]" pageId="17" pageNumber="614">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1446,1797,730,759]" pageId="17" pageNumber="614">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Not assessed on The IUCN Red List as a distinct species. The 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Dollman" authorityYear="1909" box="[1447,1516,770,799]" class="Mammalia" family="Muridae" genus="Lophuromys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="17" pageNumber="614" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="zena">Zena</taxonomicName>
Brush-furred Rat could be classified as Data Deficient; there are no records of recent captures in its presumed distribution.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
